Build instructions:
  unpack cppcheck-1.59-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
    unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport cppcheck-1.59-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/cppcheck-1.59-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/cppcheck-1.59-X.tar.bz2

